OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784220475
OL,3,CInquest into death of 14-year-old to
OL,4,Cbe reopened in legal first
OL,6,FThe inquest into the death of a 14-
OL,7,Fyear-old boy after what his mother
OL,8,Fbelieves was an online challenge gone
OL,9,Fwrong is to be re-opened after the
OL,10,Foriginal conclusion was quashed at the
OL,11,FHigh Court.
OL,13,FJools Sweeney, from Cheltenham, died
OL,14,Fin April 2022, but an inquest into his
OL,15,Fdeath in September that year lasted 23
OL,16,Fminutes and called no live evidence
OL,17,Fbefore returning a narrative
OL,18,Fconclusion.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784220475
OL,3,CInquest into death of 14-year-old to
OL,4,Cbe reopened in legal first
OL,6,FJools' mother, Ellen Roome, began a
OL,7,Flegal challenge against the senior
OL,8,Fcoroner for Gloucestershire to have
OL,9,Fthe conclusion quashed and the inquest
OL,10,Fre-opened.
OL,12,FHer lawyers told a hearing on Thursday
OL,13,Fthat new evidence had come to light
OL,14,Fconcerning the role of social media in
OL,15,FJools' death, and that a "number of
OL,16,Flines of inquiry" which were not
OL,17,Fpursued at the original inquest "bear
OL,18,Fdirectly upon TikTok's platform and
OL,19,Fthe data it holds".
OL,26,@wD@ZOUxD@QO]yD@aOU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784220475
OL,3,CInquest into death of 14-year-old to
OL,4,Cbe reopened in legal first
OL,6,FThe coroner and TikTok did not oppose
OL,7,Fthe bid to reopen the inquest.
OL,9,FAt the end of the hearing in London,
OL,10,Ftwo senior judges quashed the
OL,11,Fconclusion and ordered a new inquest
OL,12,Fto take place at a later date.
OL,14,FLord Justice Warby, sitting with Mrs
OL,15,FJustice Heather Williams, said: "We
OL,16,Fhave concluded that the application
OL,17,Fshould be granted."
OL,19,FMs Roome, who attended the hearing,
OL,20,Fwept as the judges handed down their
OL,21,Fruling.
OL,26,@wD@aOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784220475
OL,3,CInquest into death of 14-year-old to
OL,4,Cbe reopened in legal first
OL,6,FIt is the first time a child's inquest
OL,7,Fis reopened to examine social media
OL,8,Fevidence.
OL,10,FHer barrister, Harry Lambert, said in
OL,11,Fwritten submissions that the Attorney
OL,12,FGeneral gave her the go-ahead to
OL,13,Fproceed with her legal challenge in
OL,14,FMarch, with Gloucestershire Police
OL,15,Falso reviewing its investigation into
OL,16,FJools' death.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784220475
OL,3,CInquest into death of 14-year-old to
OL,4,Cbe reopened in legal first
OL,6,FHe said: "A considerable body of new
OL,7,Fevidence and a number of investigative
OL,8,Finsufficiencies have come to light, in
OL,9,Fparticular concerning the role of
OL,10,Fsocial media, and of TikTok
OL,11,Fspecifically, in the events leading to
OL,12,Fthe deceased's death."
OL,14,FHe also said that evidence from Jools'
OL,15,FTikTok data was "highly probative of
OL,16,Foveruse or addiction".
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@VO]wD@QOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784220475
OL,3,CInquest into death of 14-year-old to
OL,4,Cbe reopened in legal first
OL,6,FBut Mr Lambert continued that the re-
OL,7,Fopened inquest "could take many
OL,8,Fdirections" and that "several of the
OL,9,Fmost significant lines of inquiry that
OL,10,Fwere never pursued in 2022 have
OL,11,Fnothing to do with TikTok".
OL,13,FHe said that these included the
OL,14,Fpossibility that Jools' Instagram
OL,15,Faccount was hacked or that
OL,16,Fconversations before his death took
OL,17,Fplace on social media platforms other
OL,18,Fthan TikTok.
OL,26,@oD@POUpD@KO]pD@VOUsD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784220475
OL,3,CInquest into death of 14-year-old to
OL,4,Cbe reopened in legal first
OL,6,FMr Lambert also said that a fraudulent
OL,7,FInstagram account operated by an
OL,8,FAfrican crime gang contacted Jools
OL,9,Fshortly before his death, and that
OL,10,Fevidence from his phone found a
OL,11,F"possible attempt at extortion or
OL,12,F'sextortion'".
OL,14,FHe said: "Together, this material
OL,15,Fprovides a much fuller evidential
OL,16,Fplatform and paints a more
OL,17,Fcomprehensive and potentially
OL,18,Fdifferent picture of how the deceased
OL,19,Fcame by his death."
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@MO]vD@JOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784220475
OL,3,CInquest into death of 14-year-old to
OL,4,Cbe reopened in legal first
OL,6,FHe added: "The applicant's concern is
OL,7,Fsimply that all of these matters be
OL,8,Ffully and fearlessly investigated,
OL,9,Fwhatever the outcome.
OL,11,F"She seeks only the truth about how
OL,12,Fher son died, wherever the evidence
OL,13,Fmay lead."
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOUuD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784220475
OL,3,CInquest into death of 14-year-old to
OL,4,Cbe reopened in legal first
OL,6,FIn a statement following the High
OL,7,FCourt ruling that the inquest into 14-
OL,8,Fyear-old Jools Sweeney's death should
OL,9,Fbe reopened, his mother, Ellen Roome,
OL,10,Fsaid: "For more than four years we
OL,11,Fhave fought every single day for the
OL,12,Ftruth about what happened to our
OL,13,Fbeautiful son, Jools.
OL,26,@rD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784220475
OL,3,CInquest into death of 14-year-old to
OL,4,Cbe reopened in legal first
OL,6,F"Today, the legal system has finally
OL,7,Frecognised that there are questions
OL,8,Fwhich deserve to be answered. This
OL,9,Fjourney has broken us at times. It has
OL,10,Ftaken an enormous emotional toll on
OL,11,Four family, but we could never stop.
OL,12,FWe fought not only for Jools, but for
OL,13,Fevery family who deserves to know the
OL,14,Ftruth about how their child died.
OL,16,F"No parent should have to spend years
OL,17,Fbattling for evidence that could
OL,18,Fexplain the loss of their child.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784220475
OL,3,CInquest into death of 14-year-old to
OL,4,Cbe reopened in legal first
OL,6,F"Every bereaved family deserves to
OL,7,Fknow that every possible avenue,
OL,8,Fincluding a child's digital life, has
OL,9,Fbeen properly investigated.
OL,11,F"But our greatest hope is that one day
OL,12,Fno family has to walk this path.
OL,13,FSocial media companies must do
OL,14,Feverything in their power to stop
OL,15,Fchildren dying in the first place. No
OL,16,Fparent should ever have to bury their
OL,17,Fchild because dangerous content was
OL,18,Fallowed to reach them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784220475
OL,3,CInquest into death of 14-year-old to
OL,4,Cbe reopened in legal first
OL,6,F"This ruling means that, at last, a
OL,7,Fcoroner can examine Jools' digital
OL,8,Flife using legal powers that did not
OL,9,Fexist when he died in 2022. We hope
OL,10,Fthis is a turning point, not only in
OL,11,Ffinding the truth about Jools, but in
OL,12,Fmaking the online world safer for
OL,13,Fevery child.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784220475
OL,3,CInquest into death of 14-year-old to
OL,4,Cbe reopened in legal first
OL,6,F"To every parent facing the
OL,7,Funimaginable, please don't give up. We
OL,8,Fnever stopped fighting for our son,
OL,9,Fand today's decision shows that hope
OL,10,Fshould never be lost. If Jools' legacy
OL,11,Fhelps protect even one child or gives
OL,12,Fone family the answers they deserve,
OL,13,Fthen he will have changed the world."
OL,15,FMs Roome has campaigned for years in
OL,16,Fthe belief that harmful content on
OL,17,Fsocial media is the reason her son
OL,18,Ftook his life and sought the High
OL,19,FCourt ruling so that a new inquest
OL,20,Fcould look at digital evidence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784220475
OL,3,CInquest into death of 14-year-old to
OL,4,Cbe reopened in legal first
OL,6,FIn an interview with Good Morning
OL,7,FBritain before the outcome of the
OL,8,Fruling, she describes "not feeling
OL,9,Fstrong enough" to request digital
OL,10,Fevidence at the time of Jools' inquest
OL,12,F"It only after the inquest that I
OL,13,Fstarted to consider what may have
OL,14,Fhappened online," but she says social
OL,15,Fmedia companies refused to hand over
OL,16,Fthe data.
OL,18,F"(Social media companies) need to be
OL,19,Fworried - we cannot have children
OL,20,Fharmed and dying on their platform.
OL,26,@zD@BpmzD@Ypn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784220475
OL,3,CInquest into death of 14-year-old to
OL,4,Cbe reopened in legal first
OL,6,F"Nothing is going to bring Jools back
OL,7,Fand nothing is going to make it better
OL,8,F- but as a parent, I think I should
OL,9,Fhave a right to see if I can
OL,10,Funderstand why my child is not alive".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
